(5636, 180, -1, 3958, 180, 180, 1, '', 'Database Manager//DCS//46799', '', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Description of Work:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Administration of PostgreSQL databases in Linux/Ubuntu Operating\r\nSystem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide support in managing database replication process between IOT\r\nand Amazon Web Services environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide advice and support to PostgreSQL version upgrade and\r\nmigration process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Provide guidance in the creation and modification of standards and\r\nprocedures in utilizing PostgreSQL databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Self-motivated person providing after hours support if necessary\r\nthrough the upgrade processes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Postgres Requirements: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Four+ years database administration and programing experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; In depth knowledge of the PostgreSQL architecture and day-to-day\r\nadministration of PostgreSQL databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; One+ recent years with PostgreSQL related WAL streaming replication\r\nand query monitoring tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&bull; Performance