(5421, NULL, NULL, 3087, 0, NULL, 1, '', '43513//Applications Systems Analyst//INDOT', NULL, '<div class="ExternalClassC5072C3029044030906C29D432C439CB">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><strong><u>Description </u></strong></p>\n<p>This position will be responsible for designing and developing &#160;&#160;web-based applications in .net using Microsoft Visual Studio 2015 (C# .NET, MVC 5.0, Telerik Kendo controls, ASP.NET, ADO.net, AJAX, Bootstrap and jQuery).&#160; These business applications support all aspects of INDOT operations.&#160; The systems range in purpose from supporting early stage planning for construction projects to systems that support snowplow operations.&#160; This person will lead design and development of one or more of these systems.&#160; The person must have the ability to act as a technical lead on projects and provide guidance to beginner level developers. A successful candidate must have a thorough understanding of object-oriented concepts and a record of applying that knowledge.&#160;</p>\n<p><u>&#160;</u></p>\n<p><strong><u>Required Knowledge </u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Advanced knowledge of Object Oriented Analysis/Object Oriented Design methodologies in multi-layer architecture.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge using Repository Pattern Design and Dependency Injection Containers</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge working with Visual Studio.net 2015 technologies (C#.net, ASP.net Core, MVC 5.0, Telerik Kendo controls, ASP.net, ADO.net, AJAX )</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge on MVC5, LINQ and Entity Framework using Oracle Managed provider</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge in designing and developing MVC views, partial views, controllers, layouts, model objects, Microsoft identity security objects, dynamic routing, and MVC advanced features.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge on Performance tuning and debugging concepts using Visual Studio.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge in responsive design using HTML, CSS3 and Bootstrap technologies.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge in Java Script and jQuery.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge with designing and developing professional user interfaces</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge using JSON data thru AJAX</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge in Web API / REST using Microsoft .net technologies.</li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge in Oracle SQL, Views, Stored Packages/Procedures and Triggers</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong><u>Preferred Knowledge </u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Working knowledge in deploying and configuring a Web site in IIS (IIS 6, IIS 7).</li>\n<li>Hands-on expertise on domain modeling using UML.</li>\n<li>Working knowledge with Oracle Managed Object and ADO.net Provider objects. &#160;&#160;</li>\n<li>Knowledge in mobile application development using the cross platform technologies and phonegap API and SQL lite database.</li>\n<li>Working knowledge in Oracle PL/SQL programming</li>\n<li>Working Knowledge in Crystal reports</li>\n</ul>\n</body>\n</html></div>', '', 'CR', '', '84', '', 'Lost', 0, NULL, '', '', NULL, '2016-11-11 11:17:42', '2016-11-11 11:17:42', '2016-11-08 15:10:52', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '74', '2016-11-02 00:00:00', '<div class="ExternalClass0124676AEAA94E60AEC9B875E15EA26C"><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;padding&#58;0;list-style-type&#58;none;"><li>?&#160;&#160;7/29/2016 -dineshj</li><li style="border-bottom&#58;1px dashed #C3C3C3;padding&#58;0 0 7px 19px;">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n</body>\n</html></li></ul></div><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;padding&#58;0;list-style-type&#58;none;"><li>?&#160;&#160;7/29/2016 -dineshj</li><li style="border-bottom&#58;1px dashed #C3C3C3;padding&#58;0 0 7px 19px;">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n</body>\n</html></li></ul><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;padding&#58;0;list-style-type&#58;none;"><li>?&#160;&#160;8/11/2016 -dineshj</li><li style="border-bottom&#58;1px dashed #C3C3C3;padding&#58;0 0 7px 19px;">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n</body>\n</html></li></ul><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;pa