(5428, NULL, NULL, 3087, 0, NULL, 1, '', '43567//ISDH//Telecommunications manager', NULL, '<div class="ExternalClass8EB1D5BEBE0C43E5AEA8E6CBA196063F">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p>Please let me know if you would be interested in the below position.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Job Title&#58; Telecomminications Manager</p>\n<p>Location&#58; Indianapolis, IN</p>\n<p>Duration&#58; Long term</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Tasks and Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Telecommunication manager provides oversight for all installations and maintenance of telecommunication systems. This will require the identification/procurement/setting up hardware and installation of software. Managers is responsible for working with all departments within the agency in an effort to ensure that the overall system functions to its maximum potential.</p>\n<p>Addressing individual and departmental concerns, troubleshooting, and targeting weak spots in our telecommunication systems is a priority. Position is responsible for the following&#58;</p>\n<p>Maintenance of records on installation, repair, and replacement of parts and equipment</p>\n<p>Identification of agency''s telecommunication needs</p>\n<p>Research on the latest advances in telecommunication technology</p>\n<p>Consultation with IOT and vendors to discuss new products and upgrades</p>\n<p>Develops and administers telecommunication policies and procedures in compliance with local,&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; State and Federal government regulations.</p>\n<p>Research and recommendation to support more advanced communication systems in support of&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; both internal and external workforce members.</p>\n<p>Advanced working knowledge of VoIP telephone systems</p>\n<p>Network infrastructure</p>\n<p>Oversees development or modification of various telecommunication services or systems</p>\n<p>Reviews completed projects to ensure that objectives are met</p>\n<p>Develops and manages budgets associated 