(5435, NULL, NULL, 3087, 0, NULL, 1, '', 'Business Systems Consultant//DCS//43784', NULL, '<div class="ExternalClass9AD5AB55FC6D4D5BB2A92B665CD0D66A">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><strong><u>Essential Duties/Responsibilities&#58;</u></strong></p>\n<p><strong><u>&#160;</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Daily monitoring and updating of VMware and ZenDesk ticketing system.</li>\n<li>Daily user support and setup of Mobile devices to include training per user needs.</li>\n<li>Responsible for returns and the collection of unused State mobile devices.</li>\n<li>Responsible for tracking mobile equipment via Verizon My Biz and AT&amp;T Premier Web Sites to include name, cost center, suspensions and disconnects.</li>\n<li>Responsible for providing training guides for all Mobile devices to include IOS features and updates.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Research and analyze for identified performance improvement projects</li>\n<li>Manages the expectations of customers, stakeholders, peers, vendors and management</li>\n<li>Implement information technology requests and ensure they fit into the overall business plan for the Agency</li>\n<li>Promotes the utilization of technical services to resolve business issues</li>\n<li>Integration of new processes with existing ones and communication of changes to impacted Business Systems teams</li>\n<li>Facilitates the delivery of technical business solutions and products to customers</li>\n<li>Create and/or review drafts of documentation for written procedures and guidelines for operations</li>\n<li>Advises users through training and development of information guidelines and other communication resources</li>\n<li>Acts as a liaison between the Indiana Office of Technology and DCS users</li>\n<li>Keeps abreast of the constantly changing information technologies.</li>\n<li>Perform related duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong><u>Job Requirements&#58; </u></strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Specialized knowledge of and abili