(5446, NULL, NULL, 3087, 0, NULL, 1, '', '44040//Telecommunications Manager//ISDH', NULL, '<div class="ExternalClassBE84AD651AA84D308BF8FE079EA00D7C">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><strong>Tasks and Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>Telecommunication manager provides oversight for all installations and maintenance of telecommunication systems. This will require the identification/procurement/setting up hardware and installation of software. Managers is responsible for working with all departments within the agency in an effort to ensure that the overall system functions to its maximum potential.</p>\n<p>Addressing individual and departmental concerns, troubleshooting, and targeting weak spots in our telecommunication systems is a priority. Position is responsible for the following&#58;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Maintenance of records on installation, repair, and replacement of parts and equipment</li>\n<li>Identification of agency''s telecommunication needs</li>\n<li>Research on the latest advances in telecommunication technology</li>\n<li>Consultation with IOT and vendors to discuss new products and upgrades</li>\n<li>Develops and administers telecommunication policies and procedures in compliance with local,&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; State and Federal government regulations.</li>\n<li>Research and recommendation to support more advanced communication systems in support of&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;both internal and external workforce members.</li>\n<li>Advanced working knowledge of VoIP telephone systems</li>\n<li>Network infrastructure</li>\n<li>Oversees development or modification of various telecommunication services or systems</li>\n<li>Reviews completed projects to ensure that objectives are met</li>\n<li>Develops and manages budgets associated with agency?s telecommunication systems</li>\n<li>Works with CIO and IOT in the planning and delivery of the various telecommunication services</li>\n<li>Prepares required telecommunication requests and reports</li>\n<li>Performs other related duties as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Minimum Qualifications&#58; </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Education and Experience</strong></p>\n<p>Bachelor''s Degree in telecommunications, computer information systems, or business and two (2) years? experience, (within the past five (5) years) in a position directly responsible for design and administration of voice, data, and/or video broadband networks or any equivalent combination of education and experience.</p>\n<p><strong>Necessary Knowledge, Skills and Abilities</strong></p>\n<p>Comprehensive knowledge of telecommunication utility operations, and its related equipment, plus a demonstrated proficiency in administering communications systems. Requires accomplished computer skills, excellent organizational skills and ability to effectively coordinate with multiple project participants and subscribers.&#160;&#160; Excellent oral and written communication skills.</p>\n<p><strong>Tools and Equipment Used</strong></p>\n<p>Personal computer, including word processing, spreadsheet and database software; phone; copy and fax machine and other equipment pertaining to this position.</p>\n</body>\n</html></div>', '', 'CR', '', '60', '', 'Lost', 0, NULL, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', NULL, '2016-12-06 11:17:42', '2016-12-06 11:17:42', '2016-11-22 15:11:39', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '50', '2016-12-05 00:00:00', '<div class="ExternalClass7BE5883EA0AD4556B9A38159CC94A432"><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;padding&#58;0;list-style-type&#58;none;"><li>?&#160;&#160;8/17/2016 -dineshj</li><li style="border-bottom&#58;1px dashed #C3C3C3;padding&#58;0 0 7px 19px;">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n</body>\n</html></li></ul></div><ul style="width&#58;98%;margin&#58;0;padding&#58;0;list-style-type&#58;none;"><li>?&#160;&#160;8/17/2016 -dineshj</li><li style="border-bottom&#58;1px dashed #C3C3C3;padding&#58;0 0 7px 19px;