(5512, NULL, NULL, 3087, 0, NULL, 1, '', '45079//Systems Architect//DCS', NULL, '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p>Systems Architect</p>\n</body>\n</html>', '<div class="ExternalClass29969A63E55D4D39A324047F3C22DE68">\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><strong><u>Representative duties include</u></strong><strong>&#58;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Completes environmental analysis of system needs and requirements of existing and proposed system solutions (BPM, JAVA) and develops architectural and technical designs and specifications;</li>\n<li>Analyzes technical needs, requirements, and state of the network?s infrastructure design, integration, operations and develops documentation and diagrams;</li>\n<li>Provides direction and subject matter expertise on integration architectures and technologies such as SOA, ESB, Web Services, Micro Services, JavaScript, XML, JSON etc.;</li>\n<li>Consults with and makes recommendations to business and technical groups at all levels to evaluate architectural and functional requirements, evaluate technology needs, and formulate solutions;</li>\n<li>Creates and maintains logical and physical architecture modeling and diagrams;</li>\n<li>Evaluates technology and products to determine the feasibility of adding to CSB IT standards;</li>\n<li>Participates in and works with the vendor on system design walk-throughs for INvest;</li>\n<li>Graphically and verbally communicates application concepts;</li>\n<li>Discerns business/technical needs as it relates to child support applications;</li>\n<li>Develops and enforces architecture strategies and policies for long-term planning and implementation;</li>\n<li>Works with current Application and Data Architect on project assignments;</li>\n<li>Continues to develop working knowledge of the child support solutions;</li>\n<li>Performs other related duties as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong><u>Job Requirements</u></strong><strong>&#58;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Must have a