(5540, 1253, 23926, 3047, 1253, 1253, 1, '', 'IT Project Manager - Proj.Man._FY17_EHS-014– PMO', '', '<div><strong>Description :&nbsp;</strong></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="white-space: pre" class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>Candidate will manage, plan, organize and control operations and activities of IT Projects for the secretariat IT PMO. Duties include: Overseeing multiple projects to ensure proper management, creating and maintaining project plans, ensuring users and project team member roles and responsibilities are properly defined.&nbsp;</div><div><strong><br /></strong></div><div><p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px"><strong style="unicode-bidi: embed">Responsibilities</strong></p><ul style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px"><li>Primary initial responsibility is for management of a project. Focuses on meeting project commitments, including communications with sponsors, stakeholders, etc. Spends significant time on project management responsibilities. As assigned, lead or assist in the planning and implementation.</li><li>Work in conjunction with the Business to facilitate the definition of service levels and customer requirements. Interact with existing or potential stakeholders and the Business to determine their needs and to develop plans for improving delivery.</li><li>Support stakeholders in design, priority setting and implementation according to the Business&rsquo; strategic initiatives.</li><li>Identifies opportunities for improving and streamlining IT processes as well as eliminating security risks (compliance)</li><li>Responsible for identifying the required project resources; for their technical or functional development, performance, and/or termination during the project.</li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px"><strong style="unicode-bidi: embed">Qualifications</strong></p><ul style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px"><li>Minimum 5 years of increasingly responsible experience, including experience successfully managing various projects (in &lsquo;healthcare&rsquo; &ndash; preferred). Outstanding grasp of information technology concepts and processes. Demonstrated aptitude for effective leadership of staff. (PMP certification preferred).</li><li>Demonstrated leadership with strong organizational, presentation and customer service skills</li><li>Experience working in a PMO environment</li><li>Project Portfolio Management experience</li><li>Understanding of software development lifecycle methodologies</li><li>Demonstrated ability to conduct detailed planning, perform risk assessments, and successfully mitigate project risks</li><li>Ability to relate IT program priorities to the Business</li><li>Thorough understanding Project Management methodologies, phases, techniques and uses</li><li>Experience working in the Healthcare Industry</li><li>Experience working for State Agencies</li><li>Process redesign experience</li></ul></div>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '90', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Quincy', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-02-24 14:04:52', '2017-03-24 12:19:15', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5541, 192, -1, 3046, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Java/J2EE Developer', '', '<table border="0" cellspacing="10" cellpadding="0" width="100%" style="border: none; border-collapse: collapse; color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px"><tbody><tr><td width="24%" align="right" valign="top" style="border: none; padding: 10px">Job Description</td><td width="76%" align="left" valign="top" style="border: none; padding: 10px"><div class="ExternalClass3F76CC717CE5493482D50FCAFE738C55"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">This position is responsible for designing and developing highly scalable API''s as well as architecting analyzing, developing, testing, and supporting near-real time internal and external applications.&nbsp; External applications are comprised of several mobile and web interface applications.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">The applications are broken down as follows:</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; API Layer, public and admin web applications leverage the following combination of Java 7 (1.7.0_51), GWT 2.1.1, and GXT 2.2.1 frameworks and languages served via Apache web servers supported by a Progress 9.4 database all hosted on AWS EC2.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The mobile systems are hybrid applications built on Android and iOS.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6"><strong>Technical Requirements</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">Minimum of 5 years, deep experience with the following programming language and frameworks:</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Java/JEE solution design and custom application build experience</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Leveraging Spring frameworks (Core, Spring Cloud, Spring Boot, Spring MVC, Spring Security, etc.) and writing RESTFUL and SOAP services</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; XML technologies including DTD/XSD, XPATH, and Object XML mapping</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Using SQL (like Oracle, MySQL, etc.) and Postgres databases and persistence frameworks (like JPA, Hibernate, etc.)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2+ years of experience designing Web 2.0 solutions using technologies such as AJAX, HTML5, JavaScript (like jQuery, Amber, Angular, etc.), CSS and responsive design</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3+ years practical working experience with version control and knowledge of web deployment tools utilizing Git and associated workflows, Ansible, Chef, ANT, Apache Maven, etc.; experience &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; implementing those tools is also a big plus</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3+ years of experience utilizing Continuous Integration (CI) severs (like Hudson, Jenkins, Atlassian suite or similar) for build and process automation (CD)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2+ years working with AWS technologies and architecture is essential (e.g. EC2, SNS/SQS, API Gateway, ELB, EBS)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2+ years configuring/administering JEE application servers (Tomcat, Jetty, Weblogic, etc.)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledge of building web applications using Google Web Toolkit (GWT) and Sencha GXT is preferred</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Secure coding practices and familiarity with OWASP is a huge plus</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Familiar with developing on web based technologies to work on a multitude of browsers (i.e. IE, Firefox, Chrome, Safari, etc.) and mobile platforms (iOS, Android, etc.)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong interest and/or exposure to work in the mobile (Apple, Android, etc.) development space is a big plus, but not required</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Foundational experience in object oriented design experience, including working knowledge of utilizing various design patterns Environmental/Educational/Certification Requirements</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Demonstrated ability to work in a fast paced development environment exposed to a variety of software delivery models (Agile, Waterfall, RAD)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Acceptance to submit estimates on upcoming work and willingness to accept accountability for commitments made with regards to timeline and budget</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ability to commit to off-hour assistance and overtime required (evening/weekends) as necessary per project and troubleshooting needs</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Must continue to enhance technical knowledge and skills through research and experimentation, in-house and external classes</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proficiency with Microsoft personal productivity tools (Excel, Word, Visio) or Google for Work toolsets (Sheets, Docs, etc.) is preferred&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6"><strong>Must Have/Critical Requirements:</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Motivated self-started willing to take initiative to discover and resolve complex issues and problems</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Exceptional oral, written communication and interpersonal skills</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Able to work as a team member and willing to work independently as and when required.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong troubleshooting and problem solving skills</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.6">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Patience and desire to deliver excellent service to our organization</p></div></td></tr></tbody></table>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '75', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-02-27 10:19:05', '2017-03-24 12:16:20', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5542, 1265, -1, 2876, 1265, 1265, 1, '', 'IT Policy Analyst//OLTSS//ITS63_Data_EHS-FY17-006 OLTSS', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Requirements:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin healthcare industry and/or state agencies such as Medicaid.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">5\r\nor more years of experience as a Business / IT Policy Analyst in a Healthcare\r\nenvironment&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nwith data mining data warehouse&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">2-4\r\nyears Project Management experience including hands on experience from project\r\ninception to stabilization.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Responsibilities:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\nwith program staff to identify and document project scope&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Work\r\nas the primary lead for Business project management of IT and Business\r\ninitiatives&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Lead\r\nbusiness requirements, design, user acceptance testing, training (internal\r\n&amp; external), and implementation activities and on-going support.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Responsible\r\nfor identifying and analyzing internal process issues in an effort to implement\r\na system solution or process improvement that greatly reduces associate efforts\r\nor increase customer value.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provide\r\ntechnological consultative support for new initiatives and ensure critical\r\nsystems are in place to support OLTSS changing business needs.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage\r\ncross-functional IT related project teams by facilitating and managing group\r\nmeetings, coordinating and leading working sessions, defining and delegating\r\nassignments, and reporting on status, issues, risks and concerns.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop\r\nand maintain effective working relationships with key external and internal\r\ncustomers&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Leverage\r\nmatrix relationships to maximize partnerships to collaborate on shared goals\r\nand achieve results.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage\r\nprojects and tasks using standard project management tools and methodologies&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop\r\nand manage project plans and resources plans&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assign\r\nduties, responsibilities, and scope of authority to project team members.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Primary\r\nbusiness contact for projects that require MMIS, Claims and Data Warehouse\r\ninput&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Identify,\r\ntrack and manage project risks, issues, decisions, business process impacts and\r\ncommunicate to stakeholders to gain consensus and agreements on changes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Plan,\r\nschedule and monitor work to meet time and quality targets.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Effectively\r\ndocument and present project status, issues, and risks to facilitate decision\r\nmaking by leadership teams&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Accountable\r\nfor identifying testing needs, resources, and timelines as well as issue\r\nmanagement.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Other\r\nduties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_MailAutoSig" title="_MailAutoSig"></a><span style="font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '80', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Boston', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-02-27 15:02:03', '2017-03-24 12:18:52', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '65', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5543, 180, -1, 3958, 180, 180, 1, '', '45636//Sharepoint Developer??BMV', '', '<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Duties</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.1<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Define, document, and enforce SharePoint\r\nstandards, policies, procedures, and metrics that reflect best practices and\r\nBureau of Motor Vehicles business objectives.<span>&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.2<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Define and promote a technical and\r\nbusiness strategy for SharePoint use.<span>&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.3<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Consult with business areas, analyze\r\ncustomer requests to determine needs, and recommend, design and implement\r\nsolutions based on detailed requirements using SharePoint standard\r\nfunctionalities and needed customizations.<span>&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.4<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Schedule projects according to agency\r\npriorities. </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.5<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Develop and execute in-depth test plans,\r\nincluding end-user testing.<span>&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.6<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Support end users; troubleshoot and\r\nresolve reported issues.<span>&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.7<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Perform end-user training such that most\r\nbusiness areas are able to administer by themselves (grant user permissions and\r\nmanage content).</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.1.8<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Research and recommend technologies and\r\ntools to increase cost effectiveness, integrations, usability, and future\r\nexpandability of SharePoint services.<span>&nbsp;\r\n</span>Provide subject matter expertise as needed.<span>&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Required\r\nSkills and Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.1<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Computer Science,\r\nInformation Technology, Engineering or a related discipline</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.2<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A minimum of 4 years expertise in\r\nSharePoint administration and development with strong knowledge of SharePoint\r\n2010 and later versions</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.3<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>3 - 5 years'' experience with ASP.NET, VBScript,\r\nHTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, XML, SQL Server, Web Services, and exception\r\nhandling</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.4<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Experienced in both Waterfall and Agile\r\ndevelopment methodologies</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.5<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Developed and implemented best practices\r\nregarding SharePoint deployments and projects</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.6<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Able to analyze business process and\r\nsuggest solutions that can reduce process time and increase efficiency. </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.7<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Excellent interpersonal, written and\r\nverbal communication skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">3.2.8<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Exceptional troubleshooting skills and\r\nable to quickly assess complex problems</p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>\r\n   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>\r\n   <w:Word1