(5552, 192, -1, 3047, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Application Developer', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Key\r\nResponsibilities:</span></p><p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">Enhance </span><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">existing <a href="http://ck.net/"><span style="color: #1c1c1c; text-decoration: none">C#.NET</span></a> WPF application to support business\r\nfunctions.</span></p><p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Understand the business requirements and look for ways to optimize the\r\ndatabase management <br />\r\nprocesses, monthly and ad hoc reports, and tool sets established to support the\r\nEl program.</span></p><p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Assess existing program and data management processes and identify\r\npotential efficiency upgrades, such as translating SQL scripts into stored\r\nprocedures and converting standalone MS Access applications into integrated\r\ntools.</span></p><p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Develop SSRS reports and queries as needed and make recommendations for\r\nstreamlining / automating existing reporting processes.</span></p><p style="margin: 1.8pt 0.55in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 110%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Symbol; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.9pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: 0.7pt">Execute legacy SQL scripts to up