normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Solid understanding of Object Oriented analysis\r\nand design </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to take direction, constructive\r\ncriticism and work to specified deadlines, with the ability to execute\r\ndevelopment code with limited guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Implement programming changes to production\r\nfollowing system life cycle and release strategy procedures</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Facilitate with development within the new\r\nenvironments, utilizing the latest Microsoft stack, as needed</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Familiarity with source control software: Team\r\nFoundation Server (TFS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 22.5pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u>Skills/Abilities/Experience &amp; Qualifications</u>:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Windows/Web\r\n     Development: VB.NET 2010 and greater, ASP.NET 2010 and greater</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Database:\r\n     SQL 2014 Server and ability to work with older SQL Server versions</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Strong\r\n     proficiency in C#, with fair knowledge of the language specification</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Strong\r\n     Object Oriented design and development</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Worked\r\n     on projects with MVC 5 and above</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Enterprise\r\n     Development: .NET, XML, JSON, Web Services, WCF, Linq</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Full\r\n     stack developer (C#, VB.NET, Entity Framework/Entity Framework Core,\r\n     ASP.NET, WEBAPI, Web Services, SQL Server)</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Work\r\n     on Bootstrap is a plus</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Experience\r\n     with Agile Scrum</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '90', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Boston', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-03-27 14:55:59', '2017-05-23 05:51:16', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
