e="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Conduct\r\nfunctional and nonfunctional testing</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Troubleshoot\r\nand debug applications</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Evaluate\r\nexisting application to reprogram, update and add new features</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop\r\ntechnical documents and handbooks to accurately represent application design\r\nand code.</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '90', '', 'Interviewing Candidates', 0, 1, 'Boston', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-04-03 15:22:46', '2017-04-07 09:01:14', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5575, 1265, -1, 2876, 1265, 1265, 1, '', 'Applications Systems Analyst/Programmer', 'Applications Systems Analyst/Programmer', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><strong><u>Duties and Responsibilities:</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing">The Systems Analyst will be a Transit Applications Team\r\nmember supporting the HEAT Software Service Management upgrade.&nbsp;&nbsp; The\r\nAnalyst will be working with business users as well as the applications\r\nteam.&nbsp; Candidate will be expected to build subject matter expertise in the\r\nusers&rsquo; field and with the HEAT application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing">Duties and Responsibilities include but are not limited\r\nto: </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Meet\r\nwith internal customers/users; learn and understand their processes, workflows\r\nand business needs</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Su<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a>ccinctly write workflow descriptions, business needs and\r\ntranslate to software requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Identify\r\ngaps during the business requirements phase</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->4.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Define\r\nreport specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->5.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Alert\r\nProject Manager of scope creep that may impact the project </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->6.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Write\r\nand execute unit/functional test cases</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->7.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Maintain\r\nproject documentation</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->8.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Hands-on\r\ntechnical tasks assisting the upgrade development/configuration team</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->9.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Produce\r\ntraining manuals and provide user training</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->10.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Other\r\ntasks as necessary to move the project forward</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->11.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Analyst\r\nwill be expected to travel to MBTA sites with team members as necessary for\r\nthese duties.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->12.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Candidate\r\nwill be expected to adhere to core hours, report work accomplished, and finish\r\nassigned tasks in a timely manner</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->13.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->40\r\nhours/week; no overtime</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><strong><u>Minimum Requirements Include:</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->A\r\nBachelor&rsquo;s degree in a science, technical or business field</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Strong\r\nanalytical skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Strong\r\nlistening skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->4.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Strong\r\ncommunication skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->5.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nto easily work with all people regardless of role/title</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->6.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nto think and question people across the organization to minimize requirement\r\ngaps</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->7.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nto help bring people together to a common understanding and agreement</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->8.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nto accept constructive criticism</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->9.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Proven\r\nability to write</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->10.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Proficient\r\nat problem identification and resolution, and defining and managing business\r\nrequirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->11.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Experience\r\nproducing various work products throughout the analysis and design phases of a\r\nproject.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->12.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nand motivation to learn</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->13.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Ability\r\nto handle shifting priorities</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->14.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Three\r\nto five (3+) years systems analyst experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->15.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Three\r\nto five (3+) years application and report creation experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->16.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Technical\r\nskills including SSRS, Crystal Reports or other reporting tool</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->17.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Working\r\nknowledge of SQL and database concepts</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->18.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->CRM\r\nexperience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNoSpacing"><!--[if !supportLists]-->19.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Candidate\r\nmust bring a writing sample (i.e. software requirements, use case, or user\r\nstory) to interview.</p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '80', '', 'Cancelled', 0, 1, 'Boston', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-03-27 14:57:25', '2017-04-03 10:10:54', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
