: -0.15pt">activities and determine which activities\r\ncan be completed in parallel and in sequence.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: -0.3in; line-height: 90%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 90%; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: -0.4pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 90%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Experience\r\nin Health care domain is preferred.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: -0.3in; line-height: 85%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 85%; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: -0.4pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 85%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Have\r\nexcellent written, verbal, and interpersonal skills.</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '110', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Quincy', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-03-30 13:11:54', '2017-05-23 06:18:18', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5584, 1265, -1, 2876, 1265, 1265, 1, '', 'Business Analyst', 'Business Analyst', '<p class="MsoNormal"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Scope of Work</span></u><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participate in interface and conversion\r\n     requirement development </span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Develop test strategies, test scenarios\r\n     and test cases based on written requirements</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Execute and review test runs </span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Sign off on tested components</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Document interface requirements and\r\n     participate in their development and testing</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Document conversion requirements, if\r\n     necessary, and participate in their development and testing</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Be available to coordinate review cycles\r\n     with business users in all phases of the project</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assist in development of the\r\n     implementation strategy for the claims related subject areas </span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Support the development of end-user\r\n     training materials and end-user documentation as required.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Possible oversight role during the\r\n     stabilization phase of each release including the monitoring of system\r\n     change execution, the development of system &ldquo;fix&rdquo; strategies and the close\r\n     monitoring of the implementation of those strategies</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assist in configuration of all reference\r\n     tables.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '75', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Quincy', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', NULL, '2017-03-31 09:31:40', '2017-05-16 14:36:28', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5585, 191, -1, 3958, 191, 191, 1, '', 'Java Developer/46205/DOR', 'Java Developer with Oracle', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 107%">Java Developer</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Description of Duties:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Duties will include ongoing support of existing\r\napplications; working with business analysts on enhancements; and new\r\ndevelopment projects to build Java and/or internet applications for all\r\ncommercial motor carrier related functions. </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have 5-7 years of experience in Spring\r\nModules 2.5, (IoC, AOP, Transactions, MVC, Webflow, Security, Web Services,\r\nIntegration), Struts 2.x, Design Patterns (J2EE, GOF)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Applicant must have extensive working experience\r\nin the following: JDK 1.5/1.6,&nbsp; Hibernate\r\n3.x, J2EE 1.4, XML, Junit, log4j, JMS, HTML, JAVASCRIPT, CSS, AJAX</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Applicant must have 5-7 years in web based\r\ninformation systems development; with 3-5 years of which must be with Java on\r\nJ2EE Architecture (preferably in an Oracle 10g/11g database and weblogic\r\nenvironment).</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Support and/or develop Java J2EE applications\r\nand their integration to databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Extensive experience\r\nwith JSON, JQuery, REST and XML based web services, AJAX</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience with UI\r\ndesign and development using HTML/HTML 5, CSS/CSS3, Javascript, JQuery/YUI,\r\nAngular JS</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Must have experience\r\nwith and programming in SQL*Plus, PL/SQL, 3-tier oracle application server\r\n10g/11g, Oracle 10g/11g databases</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Desireable\r\nskills in applying Internet security design standards, knowledge of critical\r\nweb application security vulnerabilities, able to design and develop highly\r\nsecure web applications&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Skillset Requested:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Java (Advanced) &ndash; 5+ years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle (Advanced) &ndash; 5 + years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->&nbsp;</p>', '', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closed', 1, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-03-31 13:49:19', '2017-05-08 10:41:39', 0, 8, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5648, 192, -1, 3958, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Business Systems Consultant//Documentation Writer//46929//DCS', '', '<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Representative\r\nduties include</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Writes, edits and\r\nupdates CSB documentation based on requirements or guidelines; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Works with internal\r\nteams to assess and determine document design, structure and outcome;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Produces quality\r\ndocumentation and completes a quality review prior to internal team submission;\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Meets document\r\nmilestone dates and deadlines;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Communicates in a professional\r\nmanner to internal management or teams regarding status, needs, issues,\r\napproach, and recommendations;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Reviews and edits\r\ncurrent documentation for proper use of terminology, style, content, grammar,\r\npunctuation and clarity;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manages and organizes\r\nthe documentation version history and storage process;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manages the internal\r\ndocument review process;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Creates graphics,\r\ncharts, flows and reports to meet documentation requirements;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Power User for\r\nSharePoint document site(s) &ndash; configures lists, libraries, creates and\r\nmaintains permissions on the work sites;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Facilitates meetings\r\nand generates minutes, action items;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Promotes the\r\nutilization of technical functions to resolve document challenges or issues;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manages the\r\nexpectations of CSB staff, vendors, and management;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Recommends and facilitates\r\nquality improvement efforts;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">May participate in\r\nvendor procurement of technical business solutions and products;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">May train, guide, or\r\nadvise CSB staff;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs related\r\nduties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Job Requirements</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in\r\nJournalism, English, Communication, Management or equivalent;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Advanced knowledge of\r\nEnglish/technical writing processes, tools and best practices;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Advanced Microsoft\r\nWord, Excel, Visio, and PowerPoint skills;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Advanced Microsoft\r\nSharePoint document management skills (end-user/site owner);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Advanced ability to\r\ncommunicate effectively orally and in writing;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\ndocumentation management best practices;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nSystems Development Life Cycle methodologies;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Basic knowledge of\r\nproject management theories and practices and the ability to apply that\r\nknowledge;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to work with\r\nlimited supervision and high motivation;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0.9pt 0.0001pt 9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to lead,\r\nencourage and influence others to perform.</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-3 months', '60', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-16 17:45:25', '2017-06-16 10:23:23', 0, 7, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5586, 1253, -1, 3963, 1253, 1253, 1, '', 'Director of Human Resources', 'Director of Human Resources', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #3c4749; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', futura, ''URW Gothic L'', Verdana, sans-serif"><span>As a key member of the Executive Management team, the Director of Human Resources will execute a strategic role in the overall management of a large and growing multi-county, non-profit organization. The HR Director will provide the leadership, management, and vision necessary to ensure that the company has the proper systems in place to effectively grow the organization and to ensure operating efficiency. The position will oversee the development and implementation of human resources policies, programs and practices, including recruitment, selection, retention, legal compliance, employee benefits, employee relations, employment practices and procedures, employee communications and employee events.&nbsp; Reporting directly to the company&rsquo;s CFO, the Director of Human Resources will have the unique opportunity of making an immediate and lasting impact on the culture of this organization.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #3c4749; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', futura, ''URW Gothic L'', Verdana, sans-serif"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #3c4749; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', futura, ''URW Gothic L'', Verdana, sans-serif"><span>Bachelor degree required. Master&rsquo;s degree preferred.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>Minimum of five years hands-on experience in HR management and multi-site&nbsp;</span><span>environment with 200+ full-time employees. Behavioral Healthcare experience a plus,</span><span>&nbsp;but not required.&nbsp;</span><span>PHR/SPHR or CP/SCP&nbsp;highly desired.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #3c4749; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', futura, ''URW Gothic L'', Verdana, sans-serif"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>', '', 'DH', '0-6 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Kokomo', 'Indiana', 'USA', '2017-04-03 00:00:00', '2017-04-03 09:27:15', '2017-05-08 10:42:22', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
