(5594, 191, -1, 3958, 191, 191, 1, '', 'Application Systems Analyst/Programmer / Specialist/46311/DWD', '', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">General\r\nRole / Scope:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">The\r\noffice of business intelligence is responsible for benchmarking that drives\r\ndeeper understanding of agency-wide performance to best serve employers and\r\nemployees.&nbsp; This office will evaluate how\r\nthe agency is strategically interpreting and communicating data to inform\r\nperformance measures. The development of key measurements of performance for\r\nall aspects of the agency&rsquo;s business, and providing regular updates on\r\nperformance metrics will be the primary function of this office.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">This\r\noffice will regularly engage with all lead staff persons in each program and\r\nfunctional area to measure progress.&nbsp;\r\nThese programs and functions include, but are not limited to: youth\r\nprograms, regional operations, research and analysis, adult education, career\r\nand technical education, marketing and communication, employer engagement and\r\nunemployment insurance.&nbsp;&nbsp; The development\r\nof this office and key internal performance metrics will allow the agency to\r\nstreamline service to all constituents, reduce duplicative efforts, utilize\r\ndata to make strategic decisions and develop clear, comprehensive, consistent\r\nmessaging around agency priorities and effectiveness.&nbsp; Specifically:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Drive\r\nthe definition of metrics across all areas/aspects of the agency.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Develop\r\nsufficient knowledge in all data analytics technologies available within the\r\nagency to provide expertise on the most effective methods to make data\r\navailable and visible.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Own\r\naction items and resulting projects coming out of the Data Strategy project.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Develop\r\na data governance team representing each unit within the agency to regularly\r\nreview metric performance, collection, and distribution.&nbsp; This team&rsquo;s function will:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Ensure\r\nconsistency of message and impact.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Ensure\r\ndata is in the hands of the right people at the right time &ndash; internally and\r\nexternally.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Work\r\nclosely with the office of communications to ensure data is distributed to\r\nstakeholders, and considers the varying user groups.&nbsp; Develop the public face of the DDWS.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Build\r\nData Dashboard that displays regular data outcomes on internal website banner.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Requirements:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Great communication skills with ability\r\nto work across various groups of people (project team, business partners within\r\nthe agency, business partners outside the agency, etc.<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a>)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; vertical-align: middle" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Previous\r\nexperience with large data projects is preferred</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; vertical-align: middle" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Provide technical guidance or support for the development or\r\ntroubleshooting of systems.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; vertical-align: middle" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">4.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Evaluate existing systems to determine effectiveness and\r\nsuggest changes to meet organizational requirements.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; vertical-align: middle" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">5.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Develop dashboards using various data visualization products</span></p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '84.88', '', 'Closed', 1, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-04-07 09:55:43', '2017-05-08 10:39:07', 0, 9, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5604, 191, -1, 7914, 191, 191, 1, '', 'C# .Net Developer', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Top Skills Required :</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Object Oriented Programming </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Object Oriented Design Patterns </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Relational Database design and performance </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Strong experience in Api&rsquo;s (SOAP, REST, XML) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">5 years minimum experience (senior level)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Ideal candidate is a versatile developer who has hands-on\r\nexpertise in many disparate technologies (from front-end interfaces to back-end\r\nsystems), has an awareness of the full software development lifecycle, and a\r\ncuriosity and excitement for new web technologies and techniques. The position\r\nrequires a problem solving mindset as much as it requires strong technical\r\ncompetency and service-oriented design/development focus. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Seeking someone that shares client''s passion for developing software\r\nin a fast paced environment where change is never a surprise. If you love\r\nsolving challenging problems, gravitate towards collaboration, and strive for\r\nquality, then this is the job for you. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Responsibilities:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Deliver highly scalable and very robust software components </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Deliver highly scalable and robust API platform components and\r\nframeworks </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Deliver robust cloud services </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Support and maintain new and existing components and frameworks </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Drive internal adoption of new frameworks and services</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Requirements:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Strong understanding of web-based architecture in an\r\nenterprise-wide system (web servers, load balancing, caching, databases,\r\nreplication, etc.) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Understanding of web service technologies such as HTTP, REST,\r\nSOAP, WCF, RPC </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Understanding of identity providers,\r\nauthentication/authorization, and single sign-on solutions including OAuth,\r\nJWT, SAML, OpenID </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience developing cloud software services and an\r\nunderstanding of design for scalability, performance and reliability/\r\nhigh-availability </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Practical knowledge in defining, developing and maintaining REST\r\nbased interfaces; particularly those operationally critical in nature </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Deep experience in Microsoft technologies including C#, .NET,\r\nLINQ, WSE, SQL </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Adept with MSSQL, including schema design, stored procedures,\r\ntriggers, functions, views, CLR </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Familiarity with fundamentals such as object-oriented design,\r\nalgorithm design, data structures, problem solving and complexity analysis as\r\nwell as concepts such as coupling, cohesion, polymorphism, inheritance,\r\nabstraction, encapsulation, etc. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience with node.js </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Excellent debugging and problem solving skills </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience taking a leading role in building complex software\r\nsystems that have been successfully delivered to customers </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Understanding of Service Oriented Architecture and experience\r\nwith related design principles and patterns </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience with PaaS or IaaS Platforms such as Stackato, Heroku,\r\nCloudFoundry, Microsoft Azure, or Amazon Web Services </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience with caching &amp; performance optimization\r\n(Memcached, Elastic Search) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Practical knowledge creating Unit Tests </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Symbol; color: #222a35">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">Experience utilizing the following a plus: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: ''Courier New''; color: #222a35">o</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">NancyFX, Thrift, Protocol Buffers, Json.NET </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: ''Courier New''; color: #222a35">o</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">NoSQL, Redis, Hadoop, NodeJS </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: ''Courier New''; color: #222a35">o</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif; color: #222a35">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #222a35">CAS</span></p>', 'Salesforce Marketing Cloud - End Client\r\nReq from Ambassador Solutions', 'C2H', '0-6 months', '65', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-04-18 14:06:53', '2017-05-08 10:43:25', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
