ough\r\nunderstanding </span></em><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">of\r\ngeneral best practices for testing developed applications</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Thorough\r\nunderstanding </span></em><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">of\r\nenterprise security practices.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto work both independently and in a team environment, with multiple and fluid\r\ndemands.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto communicate effectively, both orally and in writing.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Mso