OBJ. Collaborating with ABAP\r\ndevelopers for customized development.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Source Sans Pro'', serif">Experience with\r\ncompleting at least one full SAP implementation in the CO module including\r\nconfiguration for costing variants, value flow in COPA, settlement structures\r\nand allocation structures.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'We are looking at $110K per year.', 'DH', '0-3 months', '', '55', 'Cancelled', 0, 1, 'Chicago', 'Illinois', 'USA', NULL, '2017-04-24 10:59:58', '2017-05-16 14:09:36', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5612, 180, -1, 3958, 180, 180, 1, '', 'DBA', 'DBA', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nDesign and implement large logical and physical Oracle databases, of a complex\r\nnature, in Unix/Linux/AIX environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nDetermine aggregation, partitioning, and indexing strategies for Oracle\r\nphysical data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nMonitor and tune database performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nAdminister end-user access and security access.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nEnsure that data is appropriately protected via database backup and related\r\nstrategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nLoad and configure process database software and application fixes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nInstall, maintain and customize Oracle Application Development Tools used to\r\ndevelopment information systems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nEvaluate and select infrastructure components.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nDesign, modify and create utilities, Windows batch, Unix and SQL custom scripts\r\nused for Oracle system maintenance, monitoring, and DASD management for tables\r\nand indexes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nProvide operational support for the database, ensuring data integrity, database\r\navailability and performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nProvide overall monitoring of the standards, procedures and integration of\r\nsystems, through database design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nConsult with and make recommendations to Information Technology Management, Application\r\nSoftware Development and Systems Technical staff to define information\r\nprocessing requirements, evaluate technology needs and formulate solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nConfer with Oracle Database technical support vendors to successfully\r\ncommunicate database problem and questions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nEvaluate technology and products to determine the feasibility of adding to\r\nagency architecture, as it relates to database administration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nInstall, maintain and customize 3rd party products, (Spectrum, Verimove, COBOL,\r\nJava) used to support information system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nMaintain Returns Processing System (RPS) system architecture including; FMW\r\nForms and reports server, Reporting, Batch and Printing, and Oracle Weblogic\r\nadministration</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nEstablish written procedures, standards and documentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nDevelop work plans for assigned projects and supervises their execution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nAssist, direct, train and review work of less experienced staff.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nIdentify, explore and recommend potential strategies for long-term planning\r\nimplementation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nWork with and provide guidance to information systems application software\r\ndevelopment staff for maximum computer utilization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nServe as project lead for database projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nProvide technical assistance to other database analyst staff.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nWork closely with management, technical and application software development\r\nstaff to ensure successful project implementation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nResolve system issues through thorough problem analysis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nCoordinate and direct multiple projects that are at various stages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nPrepare project feasibility studies, compute time and cost estimates, human\r\nresources and equipment requirements, as it relates to database administration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nComplete assigned training and other tasks as assigned by management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nPerform related duties as assigned.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nMember of the on-call, rotational support staff.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n________________________________________</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Preferred Experience:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nSeven (7) years work experience in Software Development, Maintenance, or\r\nImplementation or accredited college training in a related field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nHands-on management of single node and RAC Oracle 11g/12c databases</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nUNIX/Linux operating systems (AIX, RedHat etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nDatabase Tuning: SQL &amp; PL/SQL with excellent understanding of Oracle Cost\r\nbased optimizer</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nWorking knowledge of Oracle Golden Gate</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nExperience with Oracle Enterprise Manager 12c/13c &ndash;Grid/Cloud control</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nExperience with Bash/Shell scripting</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nStrong knowledge of Oracle Forms &amp; Reports, Weblogic, OID</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: 0.5in" class="MsoNormal">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nITIL understanding and experience</p>', '', 'DH', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Indiana', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-04-21 12:23:34', '2017-05-08 10:42:05', 0, 8, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
