(5640, 1253, -1, 2953, 1253, 1253, 1, '', 'Web Application QA', '', '<p style="margin-top: 0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.466667px">Client is looking for a candidate who is an expert in Selenium, and SQL in a .net environment. with some Manual testing experience.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Responsibilities : </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0.25in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Create robust and scalable test plans for multiple\r\nfeature components that are easily incorporated into the feature test plan and\r\nmeet business requirements;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Deliver completed test plans and test results for the\r\nmultiple feature components as scheduled;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Modifying existing tests and test plans and takes\r\nnecessary steps to fix the test(s) and ensure it meets team and company quality\r\nstandards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Gather functional and non-functional test requirement\r\nworking with business and operational team to meet the requirement and\r\nsuccessfully validate the release;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Alert development team to product design inconsistencies\r\nand deviations from standards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Conduct triage cycle for each of issue identified and\r\nfollow through the successful closure;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Work closely with the release management team to have a\r\nrelease certified and scheduled for production;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">work with the deployment and release management team to\r\nsuccessfully deploy the build in test environment and maintain the integrity of\r\nthe environments;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Provide input in developing quality assurance standards\r\nin regards to functional, regression, performance and load testing;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Ensure that the delivered overall user experience\r\nconforms to the feature objectives;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Incorporate automated testing tools and test frameworks as\r\nstandard practice;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Code functions, classes, and methods to support automated\r\ntests for HP QTP, HP Load runner, and Visual Studio; and</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Identify, analyze, and report test results for automated\r\ntest scripts using the automated test tools set;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Responsible for creating acceptance criteria and creating\r\nand tracking all software bugs during Unit, QA, UAT and Production.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.55in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Qualification: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 16.2pt 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Bachelor''s or Master''s degree in Computer Engineering,\r\nComputer Information Systems, or related field;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Two years in the position offered or as a Programmer\r\nAnalyst, Test Analyst, or related role;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">Healthcare industry knowledge preferred;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">All applicants must have demonstrated experience with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Test management tools like TFS(Test manager);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Proficient in Microsoft SQL (2012 or Greater) with skills\r\nin modification and execution of stored procedures;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Schemes and writing SQL queries and programming and\r\ndatabase fundamentals;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Experience in active adherence to SDLC methodologies such\r\nas Agile or Incremental;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Experience with Integration and User Acceptance Testing,\r\nand integrated software development tools like Microsoft Visual Studio;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Testing of client, server and RIA web based applications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 81%" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; line-height: 81%; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Validating effectiveness of user <em>experience </em>of application;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Automation and performance testing using QTP ; Selenium,\r\nLoad Runner; and</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.6in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Exposure to Big Data or Cloud development and /validation\r\nwill be a plus.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Understanding of how leading web browsers function on\r\nMobile and Desktops (Internet Explorer, Safari, Firefox and Chrome);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">Strong technical and analytical skills;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Must possess strong organizational and communication\r\nskills, both verbal and written;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Ability to work both independently and effectively in\r\nteams and a fast pace environment;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Symbol; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">Candidates must demonstrate a strong attention to detail.</span></p>', '80 % automation, 20 % manual.  Expertise in Selenium, and SQL in a .net environment. Also we need the person to have some Manual testing experience.', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Cancelled', 1, 1, 'Herndon', 'Virginia', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-10 14:19:52', '2017-06-12 10:03:35', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
