 -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->PL/SQL (Advanced) &ndash; 7+ years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle Reports (Advanced) &ndash; 7+ years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt" class="MsoNormal">Database\r\nSystems/Database Tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Oracle 10g/11g (Advanced) &ndash; 7+ years<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a></p>', '', 'C', '0-3 months', '75', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-12 14:12:45', '2017-06-29 09:58:45', 0, 8, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5643, 192, -1, 3958, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Sr. UI Developer/ DOR/46874', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Description of Duties</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The resource will work on a development/maintenance team\r\nsupporting Department of Revenue, Motor Carrier Services applications on the\r\nIntranet and Internet.&nbsp; Duties will\r\ninclude ongoing support of existing applications; working with business\r\nanalysts, enhancements to existing applications; and new development projects\r\nto build applications for all commercial motor carrier related functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Requirements are as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->5+ years working with commercial software\r\ndevelopment as a designer/developer </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Resource performs user experience research and\r\ndevelops the look and feel of the product using Balsamiq, Photoshop, Sketch,\r\nInVision etc. Prototypes in html/css/js</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-f