pan style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in building UI to accommodate multi\r\nOS mobile, tablet, and desktop devices</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability for high level of written and oral\r\ncommunication</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience working on projects using an Agile\r\nsoftware development methodology</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in developing JS templates using\r\nJQuery template, EJS, mustache</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-siz