ent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Translates\r\nbusiness needs/objectives into specific stories and related acceptance\r\ncriteria.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Responsible\r\nfor providing business and process expertise to ensure an agile team has a full\r\nunderstanding of the requirements and business objectives related to the\r\nproduct/solution being developed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Work\r\nwith your team to estimate effort to deliver client requirements and help\r\ncreate proposal/business development artifacts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Coordinate\r\ncommunication between development teams and client stakeholders regarding\r\ngoals, requirements and business needs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Collaborate\r\nwith the development team to define, design, accept and adapt features; ensure\r\neach iteration delivers expected result</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Lead\r\nAgile ceremonies with distributed design and development teams.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Work\r\nwith the Scrum Master and the team with Backlog Refinement, Sprint Planning,\r\nand Sprint Review ceremonies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Define\r\nand manage release plans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Be\r\nthe primary resource for questions about the details of the projects through\r\ninteraction with internal resources, clients, and stakeholders.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 150%" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Manage\r\nscope and client priorities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Key\r\nRequirements:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2+ Years Agile\r\nProduct Owner or Project Management experience</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience using\r\nVisual Studio TFS to manage product backlogs</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience with TFS\r\nto manage PBI''s, Queries, and Kanban</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ability to pick up\r\ntechnical and business concepts quickly</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong communication\r\nskills, both written and verbal</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Excellent\r\norganizational, time management, and project management skills</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience using\r\nVisual Studio TFS to manage product backlogs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience and\r\nunderstanding of web and mobile development technologies and trends</span><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Skillset Requested:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">Programming\r\nLanguage/Development Tools</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Java (Advanced) &ndash; 5+\r\nyears </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oracle (Advanced) &ndash;\r\n5+ years</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '70', '', 'On-Hold Or Manager reviewing resumes', 0, 1, 'indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-12 14:27:31', '2017-05-18 16:46:53', 0, 8, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
