(5645, 192, -1, 3958, 192, 192, 1, '', 'DCS - Database Manager / Administrator/46918', '', '<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Data Conversion\r\nManager</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Duties</span></u></strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Incumbent works in the\r\nDepartment of Child Services, Child Support Bureau (CSB) IT Office.&nbsp; Incumbent will manage, plan, organize, and\r\ncontrol the operations and activities of the ISETS (Indiana Support Enforcement\r\nand Tracking System)/INvest (Indiana Verification and Enforcement of Support)\r\nData Services Team.&nbsp; This Team leads data\r\nefforts including database administration, data governance/ management, data\r\nwarehouse/reporting, data quality, and data conversion activities based on\r\nstakeholder data needs.&nbsp; This role will\r\nneed to have high level understanding of all layers of the future INvest\r\napplication and be able to make decisions as business makes changes or\r\nrefinements during the project.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Representative\r\nduties include</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Establishes\r\nstrategies, objectives, initiatives, policies and procedures for all\r\nISETS/INvest data assets based on the latest data management best practices, as\r\nwell as stakeholder needs;</span><strong><u></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participates,\r\napproves and oversees the data conversion of ISETS data during the INvest\r\nproject for CSB stakeholders;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Participates,\r\napproves and oversees INvest project team on data analysis/modeling, data\r\ndesign, data quality management, data optimization, data implementation and\r\nrecovery strategy;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Guides project team\r\nin the data cleanup/profiling activities for ISETS in preparation of INvest;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures oversight of\r\nthe current use of the FSSA Data Warehouse, creation of a risk management plan\r\nand develops strategy for future business intelligence efforts;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures ISETS/INvest\r\ndatabase performance is within stakeholder requirements and monitors DBMS for\r\ncontinual improvement, normalization and integrity;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Works often with the\r\ndata architect and information security manager to ensure a consistent approach\r\nto data is utilized for all CSB applications;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures that CSB supported\r\ndatabases have well documented and updated data models, dictionaries, security,\r\nrecovery, operation maintenance plans and purge/archive procedures;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Coordinates,\r\ncommunicates and works with the Indiana Office of Technology (IOT) on database\r\nrelated projects;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Regularly meets with\r\nagency management or project leads to discuss project status, prioritization of\r\nchanges and/or enhancements, and project concerns;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Implements data\r\ngovernance practices and strategies including master data management and\r\nmeta-data;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assists in planning\r\nand estimating effort for all data tasks and activities associated with CSB\r\nISETS/INvest projects;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs supervisory activities\r\nsuch as selecting, hiring, training, coaching, assigning, scheduling,\r\ncounseling, communicating expectations, disciplining, providing performance\r\nmanagement, and enforcing policy and procedures for team;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Supports document and\r\ncontent management for data found outside of databases;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Evaluates and recommends\r\ndatabase tools to support team efforts;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs related\r\nduties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Job Requirements</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Broad knowledge in\r\nthe management of system and application database administration, data\r\nwarehouse/ business intelligence, data governance/management, data quality, data\r\nconversion and synchronization;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Broad knowledge in DAMA\r\nbest practices, tools and utilities related to supporting application data;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Broad knowledge of\r\ncapacity planning and disaster recovery;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Broad knowledge of\r\nrelational database, data warehouse design techniques and dimensional modeling\r\nprocesses;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Advanced knowledge of\r\ncomputer network/hardware/software capabilities and configurations and Systems\r\nDevelopment Lifecycle (SDLC);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Thorough knowledge of\r\nMicrosoft products such as Outlook, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, SharePoint, Project,\r\nand Visio;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Basic knowledge of\r\nIBM Rational tools;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Bachelors degree in\r\ninformation technology, management or relevant experience;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to read and\r\nunderstand complicated technical documentation and perform logic analysis;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to supervise\r\nand manage diverse human resources;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to lead,\r\nencourage and influence others to perform;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability to\r\ncommunicate effectively orally and in writing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Skillset\r\nRequired</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 27pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">IBM Mainframe - Intermediate to\r\nAdvanced - 5-8 years</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 27pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">IBM i5 - Intermediate - 3 years</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 27pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">DB2 z/OS and OS/400 - Intermediate to\r\nAdvanced - 5-8 years (other relational DB can substitute - large DB conversion\r\nexperience required).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 27pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">DB2 LUV - Intermediate - 5 years</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt 27pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">SDLC - Intermediate to Advanced - 5\r\nyears</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-right: -9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Difficulty</span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">\r\nof Work</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Employee applies\r\nestablished agency guidelines for systems development by employing project\r\nmanagement practices and techniques to insure computer systems under\r\ndevelopment for a variety of program areas are delivered per user\r\nspecifications, on time, and within the allocated budget.&nbsp; Employee exercises good technical and\r\nadministrative judgment in determining the appropriate resources and in\r\ndetermining the allocation of those resources in order to coordinate completion\r\nof a database project to meet the database project plan.&nbsp; Assignments involve managing the development\r\nof database systems that may require adoption of technologies new to the\r\nstate.&nbsp; All database projects vary in\r\ncomplexity and are situation dependent.&nbsp;\r\nEmployee must constantly monitor for potential problems and develop\r\ncontingencies for unexpected problems to insure the completion of the project\r\nwithin established timetables.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Responsibility</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Employee is provided\r\nobjectives and boundaries and is responsible for ensuring work is in compliance\r\nwith the policies, programs, and practices of the agency and IT division.&nbsp; Employee&rsquo;s work has an extensive impact on\r\nthe IT division&rsquo;s operations and other major agency programs and operations.&nbsp; Problems that may significantly impact the\r\nagency&rsquo;s operations may be discussed with the manager.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoHeader"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Personal\r\nWork Relationships</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -9pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Employee works with agency\r\nexecutive management, information technology management, division management, systems\r\nusers and agency personnel, consultants, vendors, representatives from other agencies,\r\nIOT and any other individual or group involved with the project.&nbsp; Contacts are for the purpose of directing,\r\nmanaging, supervising, problem solving, sharing, describing, troubleshooting\r\nand analyzing.&nbsp; Employee communicates\r\nprogram progress to management.</span></p>', '', 'C2H', '0-3 months', '79', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-16 11:17:06', '2017-05-26 08:50:28', 0, 7, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5666, 1253, -1, 3958, 1253, 1253, 1, '', '.NET/Angular Developer//47095//IOT', '', '<h2>Purpose of Position/Summary:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Employee\r\nworks primarily as a senior .NET developer. This resource should have at least\r\n3+ years on development exerience. The desired candidate would be heavily\r\nfocused in front end user interace and user experience development. This is a\r\nfull life cycle developer position which will include 80% new development and\r\n20% maintenance. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">We are\r\nlooking for a developer with specific skils with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">SCSS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Angular 2+ (not AngularJS)\r\n&ndash; Angular-CLI</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">TypeScript</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">.NET (C#, EntityFramework)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">NodeJS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">In addition\r\nemployee must have excellent communication and project management skills. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Essential Duties/Responsibilities</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Write and maintain code\r\nfor custom written applications</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage timelines and\r\npriorities with new feature requests.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manage the relationship\r\nbetween the customer, development group, design team, and project managers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Design new applications\r\nto meet customer&rsquo;s needs. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Interacting with\r\ndisparate systems programmatically. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Communicating with the\r\ncustomers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Deliver professional\r\nlooking apps with high usability and rich features.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Job Requirements </h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25