: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in creation of BI Publisher Reports;\r\nFRS (financial reporting studio) Reports and OTBI (Oracle Transactional\r\nBusiness Intelligence) reports in Oracle Cloud environment</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ability to take initiative to communicate,\r\ninteract, and collaborate with others to ensure that all aspects of a task are\r\naddressed</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Excellent communication skills, able to discuss\r\ntechnical &amp; functional issues/solutions, in highly escalated situations,\r\nwith executives, support &amp; customer personnel</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience in communicating and collaborating\r\nacross all levels of an organization</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Self-driven, motivated, Pro-active, well\r\no