(5652, 1253, -1, 7914, 1253, 1253, 1, '', 'Technology Architect', 'Technology Architect', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">GENERAL FUNCTION:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; color: #555555">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Makes decisions\r\non complex architecture issues. Coordinates with users to determine\r\nrequirements and design systems to fit their needs. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; color: #555555">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Ensures system\r\nimprovements are successfully implemented and monitored to increase efficiency.\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; color: #555555">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Establishes and\r\ncommunicates common goals for team members. Acts as resource for less\r\nexperienced staff.</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555"><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">The position is on the Technical/Professional ladder at level\r\n4 in the Technology Architecture discipline.<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">Responsible and accountable for risk by openly exchanging\r\nideas and opinions, elevating concerns, and personally following policies and\r\nprocedures as defined.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol; c