in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nBasic Statistical process control</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nProduct design &amp; DFMA (Design for Manufacturing &amp; Assembly)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nRisk analysis including use of FMEA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings; color: #1f4e79">&sect;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">Knowledge\r\nof ISO and GMP regulations is preferred.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings; color: #1f4e79">&sect;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">Minimum\r\nof 5 years of related manufacturing engineering experience is required.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings; color: #1f4e79">&sect;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">Eng.\r\nDegree with 6 + yrs. of experience in respective field or, Associate Degree (or\r\nextended mfg. engineering training) with 12+ years&rsquo; experience leading\r\nmanufacturing development activities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="wordsection1"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings; color: #1f4e79">&sect;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f4e79">Degreed\r\nmechanical, manufacturing, electrical&nbsp; or similar engineering genre.</span></p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '', '', 'On-Hold Or Manager reviewing resumes', 0, 1, 'Cincinnati', 'Ohio', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-19 15:14:13', '2017-05-30 17:39:20', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5656, 197, -1, 3959, 197, 197, 1, '', 'Spotfire - QBAN', '', '<p style="margin-left: 0.75in" class="MsoListParagraph"><strong>Required</strong> &ndash; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>At least 3 years of production TIBCO\r\nSpotfire support experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience installing, administering,\r\ntuning, and upgrading Spotfire 7.x on Windows Server 2012</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Multi-node installation and\r\nconfiguration of tiered Spotfire reporting platform</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience configuring the database\r\nconnections and configurations</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience with administrative\r\nactivities, such as starting, stopping, reconfiguring and monitoring Spotfire\r\nserver components</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience with clustering &amp; high\r\navailability implementation for Spotfire</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience migrating systems from test\r\nto production</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Spotfire security setup, tuning and\r\ntroubleshooting; backup and recovery</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience in trouble shooting and\r\nperformance tuning of Spotfire web servers</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Proven analytical and problem solving\r\nskills</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Ability to work in a project-based\r\nenvironment with tight dead-lines</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Customer focused with dedication to\r\ncustomer satisfaction</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Experience with best practice\r\nmethodologies such as ITIL</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Knowledge and experience with SQL/DB\r\nActivities</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>As part of the Spotfire admin team,\r\nprovide 24/7 on call support for the various enterprise systems</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in" class="MsoNormal"><strong>Nice to have</strong> &ndash; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>Oracle Business Intelligence (OBIEE)\r\n11g and 12c support experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&uuml;</span><span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif">&nbsp; </span>ETLs and data analysis experience</p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Banglore', 'Karnataka', 'India', NULL, '2017-05-19 17:22:46', '2017-05-30 17:01:48', 0, 18, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5657, 197, -1, 3959, 197, 197, 1, '', 'Appian Production Support- QBAN', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Relevant Experience in <strong><span style="background: yellow">Production Support</span></strong> of\r\n<strong><span style="background: yellow">Appian BPM</span></strong>\r\nSolution . </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Relevant Experience in BPM\r\nWorkflow Business Processes, Integration with interface and activity monitoring\r\nend to end.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Basic understanding of Cloud\r\ncomputing, SQL server database.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Exposure to Web services and\r\nIntegration Objects.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Hands on in SQL</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Experience in Incident\r\nmanagement, Change Management and Deployment Support.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Experience in health care domain\r\nwill be added advantage. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Excellent communications\r\nskills(mandatory)</span></p>', '', 'DH', '6-12 months', '', '', 'Candidate Selected/Onboarding', 0, 2, 'Bangalore', 'Karnataka', 'India', NULL, '2017-05-19 17:41:50', '2017-06-05 10:14:03', 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5658, 192, -1, 3961, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Application web Developer/OITS', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="color: #1f497d">OITS General Application\r\nDevelopment</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">A DCF application support unit\r\nis in need of a highly skilled web developer to provide additional maintenance\r\nand enhancement support its application portfolio. The portfolio consists of 56\r\napplications on a variety of platforms including .Net, Classic ASP, MicroFocus\r\nCOBOL, and ColdFusion running on SQL Server, IBM and Oracle databases.\r\nConsequently, DCF is in need of an individual with excellent technical skills\r\nincluding Visual Studio 2012 or higher, .NET 4.5, Neo4j, MS SQL Server 2012,\r\nand IBM DB2. Experience in mobile technologies and the IBM Rational Suite\r\nproducts, specifically ClearQuest and ClearCase, is preferable.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">The candidate must be available\r\nto work on site at Winewood Blvd, Tallahassee, Florida during normal business\r\nhours. Some after-hours may be necessary to support production promotions, but\r\nthis will be the exception. Office space and equipment will be provided. The\r\nwork will involve performing perfective, corrective, adaptive, and preventive\r\nmaintenance to any of the applications within the application portfolio.\r\nAbility to work well with team members is essential. The candidate should be\r\nwell versed in the software development lifecycle including requirements, design,\r\ndevelopment, testing and implementation.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Specific assignments will\r\ninclude, but not be limited to, development of a process to identify\r\nauthorization status of individuals to all 56 applications; development of a\r\nTivoli Identity Manager front-end tool for the security team; development of a\r\nFAQ for the human resource applications; and development of a DCF Equal\r\nEmployment Opportunity reporting system.</span></p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Tallahassee', 'Florida', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-22 11:57:32', '2017-05-30 14:38:17', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5659, 192, -1, 3961, 192, 192, 1, '', 'Application web Developer//OITS//EDS', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">A DCF application support unit\r\nis in need of a highly skilled web developer to provide additional maintenance\r\nand enhancement support its application portfolio. The portfolio consists of 56\r\napplications on a variety of platforms including .Net, Classic ASP, MicroFocus\r\nCOBOL, and ColdFusion running on SQL Server, IBM and Oracle databases.\r\nConsequently, DCF is in need of an individual with excellent technical skills\r\nincluding Visual Studio 2012 or higher, .NET 4.5, Neo4j, MS SQL Server 2012,\r\nand IBM DB2. Experience in mobile technologies and the IBM Rational Suite\r\nproducts, specifically ClearQuest and ClearCase, is preferable.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">The candidate must be available\r\nto work on site at Winewood Blvd, Tallahassee, Florida during normal business\r\nhours. Some after-hours may be necessary to support production promotions, but\r\nthis will be the exception. Office space and equipment will be provided. The\r\nwork will involve performing perfective, corrective, adaptive, and preventive\r\nmaintenance to any of the applications within the application portfolio.\r\nAbility to work well with team members is essential. The candidate should be\r\nwell versed in the software development lifecycle including requirements,\r\ndesign, development, testing and implementation.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: #1f497d">Specific assignments will\r\ninclude, but not be limited to, development of a process to identify\r\nauthorization status of individuals to all 56 applications; development of a\r\nTivoli Identity Manager front-end tool for the security team; development of a\r\nFAQ for the human resource applications; and development of a DCF Equal\r\nEmployment Opportunity reporting system.</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Tampa', 'Florida', 'USA', NULL, '2017-05-22 12:05:45', '2017-05-30 14:37:27', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
