(5667, 1253, -1, 7914, 1253, 1253, 1, '', 'CMM, CNC Programmer', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%">Looking for\r\nan experienced CMM/CNC Programmer with at least 10 years of experience. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%">Qualifications:\r\n</span></p><ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 12pt">Bachelors degree in Mechanical\r\n     Engineering or Manufacturing Engineering; masters preferred.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 12pt">10+ years of experience in metrology\r\n     and CMM and video measurement equipment programming.</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 12pt">Experience with Ziess Calypso,\r\n     Measure Max</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 12pt">Write\r\n     programs using Zeiss Calypso software on Spectrum CMM for Layout\r\n     Inspections</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: norm