(12124213, 191, -1, 3961, 188, 188, 1, '', 'Business Analyst FDLE #7640', 'Business Analyst', 'Business Analyst responsibilities include, but not limited to the following:<div>&nbsp;&bull; Collection, analysis, review, and documentation of business requirements&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Gathering business requirements (functional and non-functional)&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Creating and updating detailed requirements and documentation</div><div>&nbsp;&bull; Creating traceability matrices to map business requirements to test cases&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Creating use case and test case scenarios documentation&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Experience with automated test tools and creating performance and load testing/metrics&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Experience creating system, integration, and performance test plans&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Performing test case scenarios following the department methodology of development testing,\r\nSystem testing, and User Acceptance testing&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Assisting with JAD sessions with cross-jurisdictional agencies and stakeholders&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Assisting with the coordination of project deliverables&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Ensuring that proposed system architecture design, software and hardware solutions are\r\nprofessionally documented.&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Contributor to activity definition, activity sequencing, activity resource estimating, activity\r\nduration estimating, WBS development&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Contributor to risk identification, tracking, analysis&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Contributor to issue management and tracking&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Effective communication among project stakeholders&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Provide weekly status reports to the project manager&nbsp;</div><div>&bull; Assist in user training for a train-the-trainer approach</div><div>&nbsp;&bull; Ensure customer expectations are met with the project;&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;&bull; Assist with the production implementation as needed&nbsp;</div>