(12124222, 191, -1, 7914, 191, 191, 1, '', 'Java Lead with AEM', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Project Details: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Role: Java Developer with AEM</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Location: Cincinnati, OH</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Duration: Long-Term</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Visa: US Citizens &amp; Green Card Holders</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Interview Criteria: Telephonic + Skype</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Job Description:&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Work\r\nclosely with internal and external Stakeholders to build AEM solutions and\r\nTranslate business requirements into technical solutions</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Provide\r\nsolutions in integrating third-party systems with Adobe CQ/Adobe AEM as part of\r\noverall architecture</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Development\r\nexperience in Core Java, J2EE, Adobe CQ5, Restful web services and JavaScript\r\nframeworks like JQuery or Ext.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Knowledge\r\nand working experience with cross-browser and cross-platform issues (IE,\r\nFirefox, Safari, etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Demonstrate\r\nexpert problem solving capabilities to overcome design and implement\r\ncontingency to meet SLA&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Qualifications\r\nand Requirement:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Bachelor''s\r\ndegree or equivalent working experience in business, analytics, or Information\r\nTechnology Field-related field</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Minimum\r\n10 years of experience in Software Development/Engineering and 6+ years of\r\nexperience with Adobe CQ5 (AEM)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience\r\ncreating OSGI bundle, CQ5 Components, Workflow along with Proficiency in\r\nJava/J2EE skills, OOPS and design pattern</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Working\r\nexperience in Responsive Web Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Understanding\r\nof unit testing &amp; Test Driven Development (TDD)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Desired\r\nSkills &amp; Experience:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Wingdings">&Oslash;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Experience\r\ndeveloping applications using React, Angular frameworks will be a plus.</p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '', '', 'Active', 0, 1, 'Cincinnati', 'Ohio', 'USA', NULL, '2017-06-07 13:45:27', '2017-06-30 13:46:16', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124223, 1265, -1, 3961, 1265, 1265, 1, '', 'Software Configuration Engineer - DCF', 'Software Configuration Engineer', '<p class="Default"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Resumes\r\nincludes the following additional knowledge, skills, abilities and experience:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="Default"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin administration, installation, configuration and integration of IBM Rational\r\nproducts (ClearCase, ClearQuest, RequisitePro, TestManager, Rose, XDE, Robot, RUP)\r\nand CA-Endevor. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin change management using BMC&rsquo;s Footprints. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven\r\nexperience in systems management and administration of CA-Autosys. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin software configuration management. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin COBOL, Telon, Eztrieve, IMS DB/DC, JCL, Perl, Visual Basic. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Minimum\r\nof seven (7) years&rsquo; experience in Windows Network Administration and IIS. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Minimum\r\nof six (6) years&rsquo; experience in report writing using Crystal Reports. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience\r\nwith HP Webinspect software management and administration is highly desireable.\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrated\r\nability to develop, test and implement Rational product integration scripts,\r\ntriggers, build scripts, and reports. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrated\r\nability to develop, test and implement Application Program Interfaces (API) for\r\nCA-Endevor and Rational products. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrated\r\nwork experience with zOS, Red Hat Linux, Visual Age Java/Generator, Eclipse,\r\nApache Tomcat, Oracle, Sybase, UNIX, and Windows operating systems. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Demonstrated\r\nability to execute quality SCM practices for multiple project initiatives. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Proven\r\nexperience in performing Development and Quality Assurance program oversight\r\nfor SCM practices and Change Management procedures. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto develop and implement cross platform SCM architectures. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto present formal and informal report metrics, training, mentoring and\r\ntechnical assistance. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="Default"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto facilitate software/system reviews and code migrations; participate in\r\nprocess improvement efforts, including assessments, audit and post phase\r\nreviews. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph">&nbsp;</p><ul><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto work in a fast-paced, multitask environment.</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Outstanding\r\nverbal and written communication skills.</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto keep pace with ever changing technologies.</span></li><li>&middot;<span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Outstanding\r\npersonal, analytical and organizational skills.</span></li></ul><!--[if !supportLists]--><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closure Lost', 0, 1, 'Tallahassee', 'Florida', 'USA', NULL, '2017-06-08 14:41:36', '2017-06-23 10:46:29', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124224, 1265, -1, 3961, 188, 188, 1, '', 'FDC #2020 Support Technician', 'Desktop Support Technician', '<span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">The Technician&rsquo;s scope of work to be performed includes, but is not limited to, the following activities:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Configure and install software for IT user desktops and laptops; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Participate in the installation and rollout of new software packages, upgrades and new desktop hardware; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Maintain desktop software and hardware; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Support mobile workforce; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Provide Tier 2 support to IT users for basic software and hardware of end-user computing and desktop-based LAN systems; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Troubleshoot problems using scripts and checklists as guides; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Escalate to Tier 3 support when necessary; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Documents problems and resolutions; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Perform end-user training, if applicable; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Provide quality customer service; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Participate in the testing and evaluation of new desktop packages; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Implement prototypes.</span><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee"><br /></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">REQUIRED QUALIFICATIONS</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; 2+ &nbsp;years&rsquo; experience in the provision of Tier 2 Customer Support for desktop computers, printers, scanners, etc.; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Experience installing, troubleshooting, and supporting desktop applications and &nbsp;operating systems including, but not limited to, Windows OS, Office, Outlook, &amp; Internet &nbsp;Explorer; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Experience installing and troubleshooting computer hardware and software to include, but not be limited to, personal computers, printers, and peripherals in both a network and standalone environment. &nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee"><br /></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">PREFERRED SKILLS</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Solving computer problems over the phone and troubleshooting PC and peripheral-related problems; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; TCP/IP protocols; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Installing and troubleshooting 3270 emulation software; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Installing, diagnosing, and repairing hardware to include, but not be limited to, hard drives, RAM, processors, CD-RWs, DVD-RW&rsquo;s, multimedia kits, and other peripherals; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Using imaging software for deploying desktop PC&rsquo;s; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Providing VoIP phone support; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Providing VPN client support; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Working for a criminal justice agency; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Knowledge of Information Technology standards in a criminal justice environment; &nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11px; background-color: #eeeeee">&bull; Supporting end users in a criminal justice environment.</span></div>', 'We were not qualified to make submissions', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'tallahassee', 'Florida', 'USA', '2017-06-09 00:00:00', '2017-06-09 13:25:22', '2017-06-27 09:16:26', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', '2017-06-16 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124228, 1265, -1, 3961, 188, 188, 1, '', 'DCF #Unix/Linux Systems Support', 'Unix/Linux System Support', '<p class="MsoNormal">REQUIRED QUALIFICATIONS</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">a. Knowledge, skills, abilities and experience supporting\r\nsystems software maintenance</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">and system software operations for a minimum period of 3-5\r\nyears with Unix and/or</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Linux (primarily Red Hat Linux) as well as BEA Weblogic\r\nServer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">b. Knowledge, skills, abilities and experience supporting\r\nsystems software maintenance</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">and system software operations for a minimum period of 2-3\r\nyears with IBM&rsquo;s DB2</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Connect and Group 1&rsquo;s Code-1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">c. Knowledge, skills, abilities and experience supporting\r\nsystems software maintenance</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">and system software operations with the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of Capacity Management principles, concepts and\r\ntheories;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of disk management concepts and implementation;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of network services concepts and implementation;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of network security concepts and techniques;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of TCP/IP concepts and configuration;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of web server concepts and configuration;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge of backup and recovery concepts and techniques;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Ability to install and configure the Linux operating system;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Skill and ability in the administration and configuration\r\nof BEA&rsquo;s WebLogic</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Server;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill supporting IBM&rsquo;s DB2 Connect product;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill supporting Group 1&rsquo;s Code-1 Plus\r\nproduct;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill in configuring and upgrading computer\r\nsystems;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Ability to install and configure software packages under\r\nLinux/Unix;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill in hardware and software problem\r\ndetection, isolation, and</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">resolution;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill using the C programming language;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill doing Linux/Unix shell script\r\nprogramming;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill using Linux/Unix tools and utilities;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill using Linux/Unix-based performance\r\nmonitoring tools;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill using diagnostic tools;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Knowledge and skill in system and component benchmarking;</p>', '2 submissions with resumes attached & references included', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'On-Hold Or Manager reviewing resumes', 0, 1, 'tallahassee', 'Florida', 'USA', NULL, '2017-06-13 15:38:56', '2017-06-16 08:53:17', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124229, 189, -1, 3961, 188, 188, 1, '', 'DEP # 80101507  Project Manager', 'Project Manager', '<p class="MsoNormal">OVERVIEW</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">The primary functions of the selected Project Manager will\r\nbe to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Work with software developers, business\r\nanalysts, data analysts, and other technical and nontechnical subject-matter\r\nexperts to develop detailed project management plans and schedules.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Manage and monitor project progress within the\r\nconstraints of the project management plan, schedule, budget and resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Proactively identify risks and issues affecting\r\nthe project and appropriately escalate these issues, with recommendations, to\r\nsenior managers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Effectively identify change and use appropriate\r\nprotocols to manage and communication this change effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Provide status reports and briefings to project\r\nteam, customers and senior managers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Maintain ongoing and effective communications\r\namong all project stakeholders, both business and technical.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Comply with DEP&rsquo;s project management standards,\r\npolicies and processes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Effectively coordinate resources and assignments\r\namong project assignees.</p>', 'We are not "qualified" to make a submission for this position. Our bids will not be accepted for submission.', 'C', '0-3 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'tallahassee', 'Florida', 'USA', '2017-06-15 00:00:00', '2017-06-15 09:23:04', '2017-06-23 09:58:42', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', '2017-06-26 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124230, 191, -1, 3047, 188, 188, 1, '', 'Mass IT #1060 Project Manager Office 365 Migration', 'Project Manager Senior', '<div style="text-align: start; text-indent: 0px"><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Summary:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">We are looking for a PM to manage our Desktop\r\nModernization project.&nbsp; The first phase of this project focuses on Office\r\n365.&nbsp; We are close to completion of our 500 user pilot which leveraging\r\ne-mail, OneDrive for Business, SharePoint Online and Skype for Business in our\r\nnew Office 365 Tenant.&nbsp; We have multiple agencies queued for the next sets\r\nof migrations and will be running many concurrent tasks timelines.&nbsp;The\r\nProject Manager is responsible for delivering and supporting technology\r\nprojects at Mass IT.&nbsp;&nbsp;Primarily the Project Manager will serve as the\r\nprimary point of contact for assigned projects, and be responsible for the\r\noverall delivery of MassIT services.&nbsp;&nbsp;The ideal candidate is\r\nproficient in different project management methodologies such as Waterfall,\r\nAgile and Scrum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Responsibilities\r\ninclude:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Plan and manage IT projects by\r\n     identifying tasks, resources delivery timelines and success metrics.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Manage program scope, schedule,\r\n     budget and resources to successfully fulfill business and<br />\r\n     technical requirements with high customer satisfaction.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Facilitate technical support as\r\n     needed including but not limited to architectural reviews, compliance\r\n     reviews and various project artifacts.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Manage project issues and risks to\r\n     prevent potential barriers to project success.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Review with MassIT management\r\n     project schedules and milestone dates.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Interface with technical teams,\r\n     agency executives and vendors</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Create and maintain relevant\r\n     project documentation such as project charter/scope, project plans, status\r\n     reports and operational checklists.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Provide presentations as necessary\r\n     to MassIT customers, agency staff and management including use of MassIT\r\n     tools to maintain current information.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Ensure deployed solutions are\r\n     compliant with Enterprise Technology and Security Standards.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Assist with procurement necessary\r\n     to acquire goods and services to facilitate the project.</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal">Lead project meetings with\r\n     customer stakeholders and project teams on a regular basis.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Qualifications include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->5-8 years in information\r\ntechnology with at least five years in project management/IT consulting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Experience migrating\r\ndifferent business units to single, Office 365 environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Knowledge of Microsoft&rsquo;s\r\nentire cloud suite including Office, Skype for Business, Sharepoint and\r\nOneDrive</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Familiarity with\r\norganizational change management including end user training</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Certified PM (PMP) and\r\nScrum Master.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Experience creating and\r\nimplementing plans according to project goals and objectives</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Demonstrates a high degree\r\nof customer service and team work</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Ability to manage multiple\r\nprojects simultaneously</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Working knowledge of\r\nproject management concepts as defined by PMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Knowledge of Agile/Scrum\r\nconcepts</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Knowledge of ITIL concepts</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Experience working in a\r\nhighly matrixed organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Good communication skills,\r\nboth written and verbal with the ability to be respectful and diplomatic at all\r\ntimes</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">Main\r\nRequirements:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: #212121">a strong background (at\r\nleast 3-5 years in experience) in consulting.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: #212121">Enterprise project\r\nmanagement experience with the capability in executing enterprise software\r\ndeployments. Previously managed large-scale enterprise projects.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><!--[if !supportLists]-->&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: #212121">Strong written and verbal\r\ncommunication is necessary &ndash; ability to manage across diverse domains.</span></p></div>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '', '', 'Closed', 0, 1, 'Boston', 'Massachusetts', 'USA', '2017-06-22 00:00:00', '2017-06-15 09:39:55', '2017-07-05 11:48:00', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', '2017-06-29 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
