(12124232, 192, -1, 7914, 192, 192, 1, '', 'App Dev Manager', '', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">ESSENTIAL DUTIES</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">To perform this job successfully, an individual must be able to perform\r\neach essential duty satisfactorily.&nbsp;\r\nReasonable accommodation may be made to enable individuals with\r\ndisabilities to perform the essential functions.&nbsp; </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Directs the daily activities of the software\r\ndevelopers ensuring daily procedures are followed to include, but not limited\r\nto, system backups and ensuring job schedules are completed successfully and properly\r\ndocumented. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures software developers are properly\r\ntrained in relevant applications, department procedures, trouble shooting and\r\nproblem solving and ensures two-deep coverage on critical applications.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures application upgrades are well planned\r\nand executed smoothly including new feature matrix, impact assessment,\r\nconversion, testing, training, and documentation.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">4.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provides technical guidance on best practices\r\nin Java application development and is able to lead or perform complex\r\ndevelopment activities when needed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">5.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Provides administrative support for existing\r\napplications.&nbsp; Provides administrative\r\nlevel security rights to supported software while ensuring strict\r\nconfidentiality for sensitive information.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">6.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Manages vendor relationships with third party\r\nproviders.&nbsp; Ensures thorough understanding\r\nof product roadmaps; tracks and resolves problems.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">7.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Designs business solutions and documents in\r\nthe form of detailed specifications to solve complex problems taking into\r\nconsideration such factors as business processes, existing business systems,\r\ndata integrity guidelines, systems performance/capacity, and operating time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">8.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Assists in reviewing design documents for\r\ncompleteness and accuracy and ensures standards are followed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">9.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures adherence to the departmental budget.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">10.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Screens, interviews and makes recommendations for hiring\r\npotential employees.&nbsp; Coaches and\r\nprovides leadership, direction, motivation and supervision of direct\r\nreports.&nbsp; Appraises performance, provides\r\nperformance feedback, takes corrective actions and oversees training and\r\ndevelopment of staff.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">11.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Performs other duties as assigned.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">REQUIRED KNOWLEDGE, SKILLS AND ABILITIES</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The requirements listed below are representative of the knowledge,\r\nskill, and/or ability necessary to perform this job.</span></em><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"> </span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">EDUCATION\r\nand/or EXPERIENCE</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Bachelor&rsquo;s\r\ndegree (B.A. / B.S.) in Information Technology or related field or the\r\nequivalent combination of education and experience.&nbsp; At least 6 to 8 years related experience with\r\nat least 2 years supervisory experience. &nbsp;The following knowledge and skills are\r\npreferred.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">5+ years experience in </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">designing and developing Java enterprise applications using the\r\ncomplete Java stack</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience with HTML5 and CSS3 programming</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Experience with Mulesoft (or other ESB) and RESTful services&nbsp;<strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">desired</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Familiarity with software development tools for task management\r\n(Atlassian JIRA)</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Knowledge of web based UI\r\ndesign/implementation</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Knowledge and experience with agile development\r\nmethodologies</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 58.5pt; text-indent: -22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Understanding of PHP, Drupal and LAMP stack a\r\nplus</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">LANGUAGE SKILLS</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Routinely\r\nreads, interprets and analyzes scientific and technical journals, complex\r\nfinancial reports, and/or legal documents.&nbsp;\r\nRoutinely responds to inquiries or complaints from customers, regulatory\r\nagencies, or members of the business community.&nbsp;\r\nRoutinely presents information to top management, public groups, and/or\r\nboards of directors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">REASONING/PROBLEM SOLVING ABILITY</span></u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Routinely\r\nanalyzes and defines problems, establishes facts, and draws valid\r\nconclusions.&nbsp; Able to deal with nonverbal\r\nsymbolism (formulas, scientific equations, graphs, etc.). Able to interpret an\r\nextensive variety of technical instructions/information in mathematical or\r\ndiagram form and deals with several abstract and non-concrete variables.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">DECISION\r\nMAKING &amp; IMPACT OF ERRORS</span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Management &ndash;\r\nMakes decisions daily on use of resources, performance and budgets and in\r\nsupport of the organization&rsquo;s strategic direction. Decisions could require\r\nadditional expenditure of resources if not sound decisions. Decisions tend to\r\nbe short term (one year to three years) and usually moderate to high cost.<strong></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">PHYSICAL DEMANDS</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The physical demands described here are representative of those that\r\nmust be met by an employee to successfully perform the essential functions of\r\nthis job.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Able to\r\nstand and/or walk up to 35% of the time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Able to sit over\r\n70% of the time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">WORK ENVIRONMENT</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">The work environment characteristics described here are representative\r\nof those an employee encounters while performing the essential functions of\r\nthis job.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Typically works in a general office\r\nenvironment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">TRAVEL REQUIREMEN