ience\r\nbuilding APIs and API based integration between systems</span></span><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto seamlessly work in the context of multiple software development\r\nmethodologies (Agile, Iterative, Waterfall). Agile/SAFE certification a plus.</span></span><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability\r\nto be very hands on with technology</span></span><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">(specifically\r\nJava, JS,</span></span><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="spellingerror"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Mulesoft</span></span><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">)</span></span><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">is a\r\nplus</span></span><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Expertise\r\nin Integration architectures and patterns and ability to define integration\r\narchitectures for large scale software deployments</span></span><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0in; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span class="normaltextrun"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Experience\r\nin Data Analytics, Big Data platforms a plus</span></span><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; vertical-align: baseline" class="paragraph"><span class="eop"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p