(12124235, 192, -1, 3958, 192, 192, 1, '', 'ISDH //Application Systems Analyst/Programmer / Specialist/47400', '', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Purpose of Position/Summary:</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Individual selected should be capable of acting in a <strong>Team Lead/Architect</strong> role overseeing 5\r\nDevelopers supporting a complex legacy application (VB.Net web forms). While\r\nmaintaining the Legacy environment the position will also work with the\r\nbusiness unit and the team to transition to a modern web development environment\r\nutilizing MVC and then a rewrite of the application.&nbsp; In addition to leading the team the individual\r\nselected should be able to gather business requirements while acting in the\r\nrole of a Business Analyst/Project Manager in order to architect replacement\r\nsystems.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Resp<a name="_GoBack" title="_GoBack"></a>onsibilities:</span></u></strong><strong><u></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">This position will provide senior/specialist level analysis, application\r\ndevelopment and systems support for the Office of Technology and Compliance\r\nwithin the Indiana State Department of Health.&nbsp;\r\nThe ideal candidate will have an\r\nengaging personality with the ability to communicate and engage all levels of\r\nthe business unit, as well as, proven expertise in development of web\r\napplications utilizing the latest technologies.</span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif"> </span></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Incumbent\r\nwill lead a team in the support of a Legacy application, while working with the\r\nbusiness users to gather requirements for both current (legacy) and long term\r\nrequirements (new application) requiring a high degree of technical expertise\r\nand knowledge. Incumbent should be a full stack developer and must have\r\nknowledge of database design, SDLC and nTier programming architecture. &nbsp;Individual selected is expected to submit\r\nongoing technical recommendations to streamline and improve current business\r\nprocesses. Incumbent will spend a significant amount of their time with clients\r\nproviding technical leadership to ensure that business requirements are being met\r\nin a timely manner.&nbsp; Candidate should be\r\nself-starter who is comfortable working in a fast paced environment with minimal\r\nsupervision, while participating in all phases of the software development\r\nlifecycle</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Calibri Light'', sans-serif">Job Requirements: </span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Professional\r\nwork experience in an Information Technology environment with (10+) full years\r\nof application /design experience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">A Bachelor''s Degree from an accredited four-year college or university\r\nin Computer Science, Business Information systems, or a related field</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\nidentify requirements by establishing a rapport with system users or other\r\npersons in a position to understand the requirements.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Advanced\r\nknowledge of the information systems development life cycle, information\r\ntechnology, project tools and approaches to data retrieval and routing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Thorough understanding of the end-to-end software development process</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Thorough understanding </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">of general best practices for testing developed applications</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Thorough understanding </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">of enterprise security practices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to work\r\nboth independently and in a team environment, with multiple and fluid demands.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\ncommunicate effectively, both orally and in writing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\nmaintain effective and professional working relationships with internal and\r\nexternal customers, and vendors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\nprioritize projects and address immediate technical needs as they arise.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.2