perience on CSS3, JavaScript 2 and HTML 5</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Hands on experience on Angular</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Hands on experience on Responsive Single Page Applications /\r\n     Web Interfaces design and development</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Hands on experience on RESTful API integration and error\r\n     handling</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Hands on experience on UX Testing tools and frameworks</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Experience creating user flows, wireframes and mockups</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Good understanding about JavaScript frameworks like Material\r\n     framework, react framework</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Good understanding about web security</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Strong understanding and experience in practicing the user\r\n     centered design process in an agile environment</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Good understanding of asynchronous request handling, AJAX,\r\n     push notifications and web sockets</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Good understanding of browser behaviors and web performance\r\n     tuning</span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: #222222; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''">Good understanding of version control tools and continuous\r\n     integration tools</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''; color: #222222">Additional Skills:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''Open Sans''; color: #222222">Good to Have- Experience on Node, NPM-\r\nExperience on Typescript, SCSS- Knowledge on Angular 2 preferable- Good\r\nunderstanding about Selenium, Jasmin and Karma- Good understanding about oauth2\r\nor token based security</span></p>', '', 'C', '6-12 months', '', '', 'Active', 0, 1, 'Farmington Hills', 'Michigan', 'USA', NULL, '2017-06-22 12:06:32', '2017-06-27 10:03:21', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
