(12124240, 192, -1, 3958, 192, 192, 1, '', 'DCS - Project Manager / Intermediate//  47453', '', '<p style="margin-right: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Essential Duties/Responsibilities:</span></u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Understanding agency mission, vision, goals, user\r\ngroups, business processes and workflows, and how MaGIK supports the business\r\nunits.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Lead and manage </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">multiple medium to large MaGIK</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif"> project initiatives forward in a timely, efficient and effective manner\r\nto meet the agency''s strategic goals for the system as prioritized and\r\nestablished by the system''s product management framework. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures\r\nthat projects have scope defined in Project Charter/Framing documents, and\r\nproject team utilizes current systems development life cycle (SDLC) and\r\ngovernance policies and procedures;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Coordinates,\r\ndrives and monitors activities of all parties involved to ensure the project is\r\ncompleted on time, within budget, and meets quality standards;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Creates,\r\nreviews and maintains project management plans, charters, schedules,\r\ncommunication matrixes, risk/issue logs and lessons learned documentation at a\r\nminimum;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures\r\nusers and project team members roles and responsibilities on the project are\r\ndefined;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Tracks\r\nprojects using current DCS PMO tools and reports data to team and management;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Communicates\r\nproject status to appropriate management and stakeholders and addresses\r\ncost/schedule/quality issues in a timely manner;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Effectively leverage in-house and\r\nvendor development teams and business resources to achieve high quality, timely\r\nproduct releases properly aligned to the organization''s strategy and end user\r\nneeds;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ensure software requirements,\r\narchitecture, and processes are fully documented throughout the projects;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Work effectively with assigned\r\nresources and vendors to ensure completion of projects on time and on budget;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Proactively manage project risks\r\nand issues &ndash; identify and mitigate throughout project lifescycle;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Manage and maintain project plans that communicate\r\ntasks, milestones, status updates, and resource allocation;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Utilizes\r\nlessons learned to continually improve the governance and Systems Development Life\r\nCycle (SDLC) policies and procedures;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Prepares\r\nfor and facilitates meetings;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Ensures\r\nthe project delivery of software meets with stakeholder approval and quality\r\nassurance audits;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Mentors\r\nand provides guidance to lower level Project Managers;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">May\r\ntrain staff on governance policies or PM procedures;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0in -0.25in 0.0001pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">May\r\npa