em migrations and consolidations, significant business\r\narea process improvement projects and complex product installations.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; color: #333333">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ABeeZee; color: #333333">Demonstrate\r\na high level of subject matter expertise in functional area to bridge business\r\nrequirements and IT solutions; provide technical direction and ensure\r\ncompliance with best practice solutions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; color: #333333">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ABeeZee; color: #333333">Practice\r\nknowledge transfer and foster change management as the organization changes and\r\nnew skills are required, focusing on team/individual development to be a valued\r\ncontributor.</span></p>', '', 'C', '0-6 months', '60', '', 'On-Hold Or Manager reviewing resumes', 0, 1, 'Indianapolis', 'Indiana', 'USA', '2017-06-30 00:00:00', '2017-06-30 17:36:51', '2017-07-05 12:42:26', 0, 5, 0, 1, NULL, '50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(12124251, 191, -1, 2876, 188, 188, 1, '', 'Project Manager', 'IT Project Manager', '<p style="margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: normal; background: #f5f6f7" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt">Qualification and Skills</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree\r\nin Computer Science, Information Technology or related field.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">PMP and CSM\r\ncertified preferred. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">5+ years&rsquo;\r\nsupervisory experience in an IT Department.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Prefer\r\nworking knowledge of the Massachusetts Treasurer and General Receiver, State\r\nRetirement Board and/or Commonwealth of MA IT Projects. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">In-depth\r\nknowledge managing systems in a production environment and applying industry\r\nbest practices. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Excellent\r\nwritten and verbal communication skills.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\nwork regularly on-site according to schedule approved by MSRB.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Able to\r\nclearly communicate technical concepts to both technical and non-technical\r\naudiences. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Solid\r\nunderstanding of relevant technologies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Solid\r\nunderstanding of the software development process, including requirement\r\ngathering, analysis/design, development tools/technologies, release/version\r\ncontrol, contemporary testing methodologies and deployment management.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Expertise in\r\nsetting and managing customer expectations.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Strong\r\nknowledge and understanding of business needs, with the ability to establish\r\nand maintain an elevated level of customer trust and confidence.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Strong\r\ncustomer focus and ability to manage client expectations.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\ncommunicate needs and schedules to IT, MSRB staff and clients, as well as\r\nensure that plans are in place and standards are adhered to.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Strong\r\nteamwork and interpersonal skills at all management levels.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ability to\r\noperate under a dual reporting relationship (IT, customers).</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif"><br /></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 9pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt">Responsibilities and Duties</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Manages and\r\nprovides oversight to all vendors, consultants, and third-party contractors and\r\ntheir performance.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ensures that\r\nMSRB business needs are addressed in a timely manner.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Works with\r\nvendors to define continuous improvement opportunities. </span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Has overall\r\nresponsibility for planning, directing and coordinating activities pertaining\r\nto the MSRB IT vendors.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Manage\r\nauthorized budget appropriations and expenditures. </span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Ensures that\r\nproject goals are accomplished and in line with MSRB/Treasury IT objectives.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Is\r\nresponsible for managing the IT consultant team that develops and carries out\r\ninternal MSRB IT projects. </span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Works\r\nclosely with the user community (and through business technologists) in\r\ndetermining how technology might assist in addressing their needs, and then\r\ntranslates these needs into system requirements and design specifications with\r\nthe vendors. </span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Understands\r\nhow to leverage applications for competitive advantage.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Manages a\r\ndynamic team of IT contractors who constantly search for creative ways to\r\nelevate the capabilities of technology systems to meet business needs, partly\r\nby capitalizing on emerging technologies and partly by adapting technologies to\r\nthe needs of MSRB. </span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Provides\r\ntechnology strategy planning.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Integrates\r\ninformation technologies into business for optimal effectiveness.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Understands\r\ncurrent and future business goals and ongoing IT issues to ensure business\r\nsuccess.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif">Consults\r\nwith management and reviews project proposals to determine goals, time frame,\r\nfunding limitations, procedures for accomplishing projects, staffing\r\nrequirements and allotment of resources and provides recommendations to MSRB\r\nExecutive Director and/or his/her designee.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in" class="MsoListBullet"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Symbol">&middot;<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;